  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0874637cabf445b44aa6cb3553862f49, type: 3}
  m_Name: Telinga_3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::PenyakitData
  tagBahagian: Telinga
  namaPenyakit: Ear Mites (Otodectes cynotis)
  namaPenyakitEN: Ear Mites (Otodectes cynotis)
  tahapRisiko: Tahap 1
  tahapRisikoEN: Level 1
  gambar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 189176aea096b2544b472eaa2393ba22, type: 3}
  isGraphic: 0
  punca: Jangkitan parasit hama Otodectes cynotis.
  simptom: Terdapat lelehan kotoran hitam (seperti kopi) dalam telinga dan kucing
    sangat kerap menggaru.
  tindakan: Bersihkan telinga secara berkala dan elakkan kontak dengan kucing yang
    dijangkiti.
  maklumatTambahan: Ia mungkin nampak seperti tahi telinga biasa dan tak hilang walaupun
    dibasuh. Jika guna kapas, ia berwarna sangat gelap. Pastikan alat pencuci telinga
    disanitasi.
  puncaEN: Infection by the parasite mite Otodectes cynotis.
  simptomEN: Presence of black discharge (like coffee grounds) inside the ear and
    the cat scratches very frequently.
  tindakanEN: Clean the ears regularly and avoid contact with infected cats.
  maklumatTambahanEN: It might look like normal earwax and does not go away even
    when washed. If using cotton, it appears very dark in color. Ensure the ear cleaning
    tools are sanitized.
